Subject: [PATCH 12/19] feat(api): process session slash commands

Add opt-in command handling for API session chat routes so /model can update the session model without running an agent turn. Persist non-secret model runtime metadata for future turns and cover JSON and SSE paths.

Co-authored-by: Nako <280596805+nakoagent@users.noreply.github.com>

